data.description: Contact the listing agent, or your agent, to schedule a virtual walk-thru tour of this home, or for a link to view a walk-thru tour. BEAUTIFUL NEW DIMENSIONAL SHINGLE ROOF AS OF JULY 2019! ALL NEW 6'' GUTTERS AND DOWNSPOUTS AS OF JUNE 2019. NEW EXTERIOR STAIN AND TRIM AS OF JUNE 2019. NEW 3 TON AIR CONDITIONER AS PART OF DUAL HVAC SYSTEM AS OF DECEMBER 2019. Immediately feel at one with nature as you enter this private and peaceful country executive estate that feels like a retreat every day of the year. The long drive passes through a beautifully wooded acreage and by the large stocked fishing pond before depositing you in front of the beautiful custom built home that is constructed of easy care cypress and has been freshly painted. Enter the home either through the front door to the far. Every room is thoughtfully designed to integrate you with the natural beauty of the property and the easy functionality of the home. This structure is full of natural light with large front and rear windows, vaulted ceilings and an open concept that is welcoming to multiple activities. There are many areas that invite relaxation and conversation for all your special holidays and occasions. The living room has a vaulted ceiling and beautiful wood burning fireplace with original Buckstove insert and custom oak mantle. The unique front solarium is perfect for having your morning coffee. The rear family room has another vaulted ceiling and walls of glass which is great for relaxing with a good book or walk out through French doors on either side to the large top wrap deck for nature-watching, a lazy evening of conversation around the fire pit or hot tub therapy! The side living room also has access to the top deck through another matching French door. There is a private office to the right of the front door.
